      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Problem is solved. The above works.\nThis is a temp sweep from 15C to 50C (realistic operating range) with VDD from 3 to 5.  Typical corner. And this goes from 31uA to 37uA.\nSweeping across all transitor and resistor corners and vdd and temp, I get from 22uA to 55uA which is good enough for this application.",
